title: Cyanide and Happiness - Complete through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"CYANIDE AND HAPPINESS" Web Comic

"Cyanide and Happiness" (explosm.net) by Rob DenBleyker, Kris Wilson, Dave McElfatrick and Matt Melvin is a popular stick figure gag-a-day Web comic that started running daily in January 2005.  The comic's authors attribute much of its success to its often controversial nature.

This torrent compiles "Cyanide and Happiness" comics into a set of CBR files, one for each year, starting with 2005 and running through 2014.  It includes only the actual comics; it doesn't include the series' animated shorts
